Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊～我的搜！啊-\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Aaah! {\i} {\i1}My hand! Aah--{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}沙滩镇得救了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Beach City was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是谁是幕后英雄？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}女士！-蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Miss! Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.29,0:02:52.29,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(220,850)}珊迪\N恐怖电影爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你认为是谁拯救了沙滩镇\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who do you think saved Beach City
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}解决了太空巨掌？\N{\fnArial\fs48}from the giant hand craft?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦。嘿，罗尔纳多\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Hey, Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等。这是-你在录像吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. A-- are you filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}请回答问题\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦。好吧。呃，当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Okay. Um, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁拯救了我们？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who saved us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，好吧，难道不是史蒂文...的家人？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, well, wasn't it Steven's...Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我认为她们不喜欢与人接触\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I think they pretty much keep to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文说她们在保护地球与人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven says they protect the planet and the human race
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且她们有魔力\N{\fnArial\fs48} And that they have magic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这听起来难以置信\N{\fnArial\fs48}It sounds hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我看到过不少疯狂的事\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I've seen some pretty wild stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.65,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220,850)}奇奇\N披萨家嗣女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一次，她们为我们做了汉堡包\N{\fnArial\fs48}Once, they made us hamburgers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们相处的很愉快\N{\fnArial\fs48}and we were having a pretty good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但接着我们遭到一个巨大生物的攻击\N{\fnArial\fs48}But then we were attacked by a huge creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！你在拍电影吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey! You making a movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.25,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(1650,850)}珍妮\N令人生畏的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，别打扰他\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是关于宝石战队的“网录片”\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a docu-web-umentary about The Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们疯！了！\N{\fnArial\fs48} They are c-ra-zy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们中的一个还差点打到我脸\N{\fnArial\fs48}One of them tried to knock me in the face.
Dialogue: 600,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.96,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}详见第二季第2集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我并不生她们的气\N{\fnArial\fs48}I ain't mad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}杜威市长，您认为是谁\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mayor Dewey, who do {\i1}you{\i} think
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.33,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(520,850)}杜威市长\N杜威市长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}将沙滩市从巨掌下拯救\N{\fnArial\fs48}saved Beach City from the hand craft?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？年轻人，我将此归功于选民们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why, young man, I credit the voters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是他们拯救了沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs48}with saving Beach City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的选民们知道他们任命了\N{\fnArial\fs48}My constituents know they've elected a mayor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可以信赖的市长\N{\fnArial\fs48}whom they can trust to --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？不，我是指水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}huh? No, I'm talking about The Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为-为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48} W-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我在报道一个故事\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I'm covering the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}遮掩？！什么遮掩？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cover-up?! What cover-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，市长-保安！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But, mayor -- security!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:00.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！你掩盖不了真相！\N{\fnArial\fs48}H-hey! You can't suppress the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}显然，水晶战士背景复杂\N{\fnArial\fs48}Obviously, The Crystal Gems were involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}甚至与政府最高层有一腿\N{\fnArial\fs48}even at the highest levels of local government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我决定追根溯源\N{\fnArial\fs48}I decided to go to the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在，我站在-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right now, I'm standi--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}大声点！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在，我就站在\N{\fnArial\fs48} Right now, I'm standing directly below
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水晶战士的城堡下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}the fortress of The Crystal Gems!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:22.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我将尝试进行接触\N{\fnArial\fs48}I am now going to attempt to make contact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}神秘，隐蔽和-\N{\fnArial\fs48}with the mysterious, reclusive, and --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！嗨，罗尔纳多\N{\fnArial\fs48}aah! Hi, Ronaldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，嗨，佩迪。那是个相机？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, hi, peedee. Is that a camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对。我们在做一部影片，关于-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. We're making a movie about --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是一部调查报告，纪实摄影\N{\fnArial\fs48}it's an investigative report, shot camera vérité.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}酷！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:42.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么...想参与惊天大采访吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So...Want to participate in a groundbreaking interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}除非你肯...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Only if {\i1}you...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:49.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}参与一杯鲜榨柠檬汁！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Participate in a glass of fresh-squeezed lemonade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢～。那个巨掌？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ohhh. That giant hand?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.80,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(1500,850)}史蒂文\N热情的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是一个来抓我们的太空船\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was a spaceship coming to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们？！我就知道！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Us?! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，我们知道的太多了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, we know too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不是“我们”\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, not {\i1}us{\i} us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是指我和水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I meant me and The Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等。所以巨掌并不是来抓人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. So the hand wasn't here to snatch up humans
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}组建人类动物园？\N{\fnArial\fs48}for a human zoo?
Dialogue: 600,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.25,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}Ronaldo立Flag的水平真是超一流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者干预我们有补贴的沙滩市风力电厂？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Or interfere with our subsidized Beach City wind farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者解冻“1%”的冷冻宠物\N{\fnArial\fs48}Or thaw the cryogenically frozen pets of the one percent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...不，我很确定\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh... No, I'm pretty sure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它来沙滩市是为了我和水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}it came to Beach City for me and The Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以如果你和水晶战士不在这\N{\fnArial\fs48}So if you and The Crystal Gems weren't here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们就不会被巨掌攻击了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}we wouldn't have been attacked by the giant hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢。肯定不会\N{\fnArial\fs48} Ohh. Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当！当！当！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And there it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水晶战士并没有拯救我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}The Crystal Gems weren't saving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们令我们处于危险之中\N{\fnArial\fs48}They were putting us in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我感到别无选择\N{\fnArial\fs48}I felt I had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:42.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只能赤裸裸地将这丑恶的事实\N{\fnArial\fs48}but to lay bare this ugly truth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}展现给不知情的沙滩镇居民\N{\fnArial\fs48}to the unwitting citizens of Beach City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}女士！\N{\fnArial\fs48}:Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you aware that The Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不仅拯救了小镇\N{\fnArial\fs48}not only saved the town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但同时也是导致入侵的原因？\N{\fnArial\fs48}but also {\i1}caused{\i} the invasion in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢。嗯...反正再没有鱼从手里滑掉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Well, no more fish are getting knocked out of my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以我没什么好抱怨的\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}先生！先生！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.04,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(260,850)}洋葱头\N？？？？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你对水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do you feel about The Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}吸引危险外星生物袭击的事有什么看法？\N{\fnArial\fs48}attracting an onslaught of dangerous space beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你感觉安全吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you feel safe?
Dialogue: 600,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.04,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处洋葱头的举动影射了很多动画节目中寡言角色在规避对话时的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！你不可能永远保持沉默！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey! You can't keep quiet forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:11.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么能安然生活，明知我们正遭受\N{\fnArial\fs48}How can you possibly go on, knowing that we are under siege
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.28,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(1600,850)}爸爸\N监制人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}意图打倒水晶战士的力量的围攻？\N{\fnArial\fs48}by forces meant to destroy The Crystal Gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还有多久完成这个项目？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How close are you to being done with this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}回答问题，爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just answer the question, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我觉得挺遭的\N{\fnArial\fs48} I-I guess it's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但像我这样的普通人又能做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But what's a regular guy like me supposed to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我还有工作要完成\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且你也是！放下相机！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And so do you! Put down that camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}每个人都过于害怕\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everyone was too afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:35.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}意识到他们实际上很害怕\N{\fnArial\fs48}to realize they were actually afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}沙滩镇需要一个英雄\N{\fnArial\fs48}Beach City needed a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且那个英雄必须是我\N{\fnArial\fs48}And that hero would have to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Whoa, whoa --{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}OK，都准备好了\N{\fnArial\fs48}okay, everything's ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可以开始我们的夜间潜入活动报道\N{\fnArial\fs48}for our full-on nighttime stealth coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们这样真的好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is it really okay for us to be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}像这样在这里瞎逛？\N{\fnArial\fs48}lurking around here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不是瞎逛！我们在调查！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're not lurking! We're investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是见证勇气的时刻\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is a moment of true bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你像我一样勇敢吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you brave like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我足够勇敢到做这件事\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm so brave to be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}回去，弟弟！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stay back, little bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}比比谁先回到危险区\N{\fnArial\fs48}Race you back to the danger zone.
Dialogue: 600,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.34,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}Amethyst的话源自电影《壮志凌云》主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等！-史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait up! Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，嘿，罗尔纳多。嘿，佩迪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, hey, Ronaldo. Hey, peedee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们应该小心-\N{\fnArial\fs48}You guys should be careful --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别开玩笑了！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Cut the pleasantries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们都是我们市的危险因素！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're all a danger to our city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在说什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠！现在！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，天辣噜！那是个什么鬼东西？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hohhh, my gosh! What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠！现在！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Pearl! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！瞄着眼睛！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha! Aim for the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好的，石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aye-aye, Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where's Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在这！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们完成这个任务吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这正是我说的，史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is exactly the kind of thing I'm talking about, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但水晶战士是来帮助人们的\N{\fnArial\fs48}But The Crystal Gems are here to {\i1}help{\i} people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但所有的怪物只因为你们\N{\fnArial\fs48}But all the monsters just come here to get {\i1}you{\i} guys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}同时四处破坏，让我们处于危险\N{\fnArial\fs48}and then wreck things and put us in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}沙滩市如果没有你们会安全很多！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Beach City would be way safer if you guys weren't here!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.75,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}{\pos(1630,850)}水晶战士\N沙滩市没有他们会更安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着 ，薯条仔，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Listen, frybo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}魔法生物确实是被我们吸引过来的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Magic beings are indeed drawn to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:55.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我们在沙滩市存在前很久就来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but we were here long before Beach City even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁在乎你们呆在这里有多久？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who cares how long you've been here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}无辜的人将一直处于危险之中\N{\fnArial\fs48}Innocent people are in danger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只要你们还在这里！\N{\fnArial\fs48}as long as you're hanging around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:03.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你说的对。我觉得我们还是离开吧。\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're right. I guess we'll just leave, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等？真的？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Excuse me? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，石榴-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But, Garnet --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别但是了，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}put your buts away, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们在这里不受欢迎，那么我们就走呗。\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're not wanted here, so let's just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，石榴，我们得搬运所有的泡泡\N{\fnArial\fs48}But, Garnet, we'll have to move all the bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而-而且史蒂文的东西呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}A-and what about Steven's things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}天！我还挺喜欢这的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Man! Ugh. I kind of liked it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:22.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}任务完成！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mission accomplished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，你可以把摄像机转向-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, you can turn the camera o--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊....\N{\fnArial\fs48}ahhhhh.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.12,0:08:27.12,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,850)}罗尔纳多\N成功的纪录片导演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}恩，是的。我做到了。\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's right. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}多亏了我，那些宝石人永远的离开了这个小镇\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks to me, the gems are gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真是太在了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在已没有可以发博客的内容了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now you won't have anything to blog about anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}拜托，兄弟。我给影片结尾呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, dude. I'm trying to finish the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，这和你的影片有关\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, this {\i1}relates{\i} {\i1}to your movie.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你自己说的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You said it yourself --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石人是沙滩镇一切奇特事物的源头\N{\fnArial\fs48}the gems cause all the weird stuff in Beach City,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以现在他们离开了，也就不会有什么奇怪的东西了。\N{\fnArial\fs48}so now that they're gone, there'll be no more weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我做了什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-做了-什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What {\i1}had{\i} I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我搞砸了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I done bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我犯了一个大错\N{\fnArial\fs48}I made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这可是“异死攸关"的大事！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is a matter of weird and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我...不能跑的再快了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm going... As fast as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水晶战士！你们一定要留下来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Crystal gems! You have to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们存在导致的每场混乱\N{\fnArial\fs48}Every messed-up consequence of your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是我每天起床的理由！\N{\fnArial\fs48}gives me reason to wake up in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没有你们，我的博客就毁了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Without you, my blog doesn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我太晚了！我都做了什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm too late! What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我让沙滩市...\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've made Beach City...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}正常了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:27.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我打破了我对小镇的誓言！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've broken my promise to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有对我自己的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们还在！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}求求你别走！我错了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please don't leave! I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}留下来并继续让这个小镇怪异吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stay and keep this town weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我完全没有头绪\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:46.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不知水晶战士会如何回应我的请求\N{\fnArial\fs48}how this Crystal Gem would respond to my plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}答案你绝对想不到\N{\fnArial\fs48}The answer will shock you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Haaaaaaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:56.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢！谢谢！谢谢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:06.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我熟练的说服宝石人留下来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had skillfully negotiated for the gems to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许我以后可以做...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Perhaps I have a future in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}星际外交官？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Intergalactic diplomacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最后，\N{\fnArial\fs48}In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得宝石人们确实拯救了沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs48}I suppose the gems really do save Beach City --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}免其毫无异象！\N{\fnArial\fs48}from being not weird!
